high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk over to the window, turn left again and walk over to the wall then turn left to face the wooden table.
Pick up the rightmost box of tissues off of the wooden table.
Turn around and walk up to the wall, then turn right and walk around the wooden table to the small black table to the left of the bed.
Put the tissue box on the small black table to the left of the lamp.
Turn left and walk towards the chair, then turn left and walk forward, turn right and walk up to the window then turn left and walk over to the wooden table.
Pick up the box of tissues that is closest to the discs on the wooden table.
Turn left and walk over to the small black table to the left of the bed.
Put the tissue box on the small black table to the left of the tissue box that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two tissue boxes to a small black table.

high_descs: Walk around to the other side of the table.
Pick up the tissue box furthest to the right.
Turn left and veer right to the nightstand by the bed.
Place the tissue box on the nightstand to the left of the lamp.
Turn around and walk back to the side of the table with the chair.
Pick up the closest tissue box.
Turn left and veer back to the nightstand by the bed.
Place the tissue box on the nightstand to the left of the other tissue box.
anns.task_desc: Place two tissue boxes on the nightstand.

high_descs: turn right, go around dining table to right side of chair
pick up tissues on dining table closest to dining chair
turn left, go to black bedside table with lamp to the right
place tissue box on the bedside table to the left of lamp
turn around, go to back side of dining chair
pick up tissue box in center of dining table
turn left, go to black bedside table with lamp and tissues to the right
place tissue box upright on bedside table to the left of tissue box
anns.task_desc: Place two tissue boxes on bedside table to the left of lamp
